<body>
<p>Ye Olde Ice Cream Shoppe has</p>
<ul>
  <li>three sizes: large, extra large, and humongous.</li>
  <li>four flavors: chocolate pudding, pumpkin, rum raisin, and ginger.</li>
  <li>two containers: cone and cup.</li>
</ul>
<p>How many different single-flavor things can you order?</p>
<ul>
  <li>Extra large chocolate pudding cone</li>
  <li>Humongous pumpkin cup</li>
  <li>...</li>
</ul>
<p>Your mission is to write a <code>menu</code> block that takes as input a list of lists indicating all the choices to make, and reports a list of sentences with all the possibilities:</p>
<p><img src="/bjc-r/img/recur/reporters/menu-example.png" alt="menu example" /></p>
